<dt><font size="-1">07/04/2011</font></dt>
<dt><a href="episodes/episode_67.mp3"><font size="+2">Episode 67: Origins 2011</font></a></dt>
<font size="+1">
<dd>
We discuss our time at Origins this year.
Coverage of the Origins Award winners.
The great white buffalo.
It was a great show overall, but with a much different atmosphere.
</dd>
<br>
