<dt><font size="-1">04/18/2011</font></dt>
<dt><a href="episodes/episode_65.mp3"><font size="+2">Episode 65: It was Fated</font></a></dt>
<font size="+1">
<dd>
Rich and Earl discuss the Fate v3 system and the Dresden Files RPG.
They provide an overview of the game and how you can bolt it on to any other RPG
and gain a more rewarding experience.
</dd>
<br>
<dt>Cast:
<a class="SUBMENU" href="/about.php#rich">Rich</a>
<a class="SUBMENU" href="/about.php#earl"> and Earl</a>
